sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (React/Vite)
    participant API as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant V as Gemini Validation Model
    participant G as Gemini Generation Model
    participant D as Gemini Director Prompt Step
    participant T as Gemini TTS Model

    U->>FE: Enter Japanese word + click Analyze
    FE->>API: POST /api/word/analyze { word }

    API->>API: normalize_word()
    alt Empty after normalize
        API-->>FE: 400 Word must not be empty
        FE-->>U: Show error
    else Not Japanese chars
        API-->>FE: validation.is_valid = false (local rule)
        FE-->>U: Show validation reason
    else Japanese chars
        API->>V: validate_word(word)
        V-->>API: { is_valid, reason }

        alt Validation invalid
            API-->>FE: validation only (no content/audio)
            FE-->>U: Show validation reason
        else Validation valid
            API->>G: explanation_prompt(word)
            G-->>API: explanation { meaning, usage }

            API->>G: dialogues_prompt(word, usage)
            G-->>API: dialogues[2 scenarios]

            loop each scenario
                API->>D: director_prompt(word, title, context, transcript)
                alt Director succeeds
                    D-->>API: directed_tts_prompt + style_notes
                else Director fails
                    API->>API: fallback to basic transcript TTS text
                end

                API->>T: generate_content(AUDIO, tts_text)
                T-->>API: inline audio bytes
                API->>API: normalize MIME / PCM->WAV if needed
            end

            API-->>FE: validation + explanation + dialogues + audio + directed_prompts
            FE-->>U: Render explanation/dialogues/audio
        end
    end